18.description:
AQUA Exploración is at the forefront of delivering autonomous and remote integrated solutions, products, and services to meet the diverse needs of the global subsea industry. With a rich history of excellence, we offer a comprehensive suite of subsea solutions, including Subsea Robotics, hydrography, Geophysical, Seismic 2D, and Inspection, Maintenance, and Repair (IMR) services.

Our capabilities extend from data acquisition to post-processing, ensuring seamless deliverables to our end clients. With a team boasting decades of industry experience, we are continuously pioneering new and innovative approaches to project execution.

Operating within a demanding sector, AQUA Exploración prioritizes the safety and well-being of all individuals involved in our operations, fostering a secure and accident-free work environment. Upholding rigorous environmental standards, we actively champion pollution prevention, underscoring our commitment to environmental stewardship.

Specializing in offshore services within the Energy industry, our primary office is strategically located in Ciudad Del Carmen, Campeche. AQUA Exploración stands as a trusted and highly effective partner in the provision of offshore solutions.
